data.description: Welcome to this stunning 2021 home in the heart of Erwin. This charming ranch boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 baths with a one car garage. Step inside and be captivated by the luxury of 6'' plank flooring that flows seamlessly throughout the open-concept living spaces. A fenced-in backyard, perfect for relaxation and entertaining.
